Acceptance Criteria — last bullet ('The final project rubric retains every structural marker specified by `immune-floury-toad`')","norm_id":"n741095c74fddd072","priority":0.2063,"reason":"veto:absence-refuted","scenarios":["An executor implementing AC 15 cannot know which rubric lines are 'structural markers' without locating and reading the external spec, which is unspecified.","A reviewer checking completeness cannot confirm the rubric is compliant without the same missing pointer."],"severity":"major","suggested_fix":"Either inline the required markers directly in the AC (e.g. 'rubric retains: `### Criterion`, `### Must-fire cases`, `#### Alternate shapes` sections') or add a parenthetical: '(see `docs/criterion-spec-immune-floury-toad.md` for the marker list)'.","tier":"LLM","validity":0.375,"verification":{"binary":{"absence_confirmed_in_context":"no","cited_reference_accurate":"yes","claims_absence":"yes","committed_work_relies_on_unbacked_claim":"na","evidence_entails_finding":"no","impact_follows_necessarily":"no","is_verifiable":"yes","no_existing_mitigation":"no","no_viable_alternative_explanation":"no","path_reachable":"yes","respects_artifact_altitude":"yes","severity_claim_justified":"no"},"severity_attributes":{"ac_unverifiable":"underspecified_oracle","blast_radius":"local","debt_impact":"low","divergent_implementation":"none","dod_uncertifiable":"none","internal_conflict":"none","irreversible_without_rationale":"none","likelihood":"low","prod_impact":"none","reversibility":"easy","silent_vs_self_revealing":"","undecomposed":"none","vague_directive":"low"}}},{"block_threshold":0.6,"blocking_enabled":true,"checklist_item":"- [ ] Either add `tests/unit/test_project_portability_criterion.py` to the Scope (if this plan creates or owns it) or move the reference to an explicit dependency in the Dependencies section and confirm the sibling task delivers it before this plan's final AC is checked.","cohort":["COH","E1","T4"],"criteria":["E1","COH"],"decision":